<h3>Zagorski soup</h3>
<p><p>Zagorski is a Hungarian spin on Zagorska,  which refers to the region of Zagorje in Croatia, where the capital city Zagreb is also found. This classic soup is a bit savoury but serves as a great starter before cevapi. Having steaming hot, cheesy scones on the side is a must.</p>
</p>
<a href="/guide/cookbook/soups/2021/01/24/zagorski.html" class="mybtnguide">Open zagorski soup recipe</a>

<h3>Creamy pea soup</h3>
<p><p>One of the creamy soups when you need something quick and light. Green pea is the protagonist of this soup.</p>
</p>
<a href="/guide/cookbook/soups/2020/12/30/creamy-pea.html" class="mybtnguide">Open creamy pea soup recipe</a>

